<h3 class="term-title">A BETTER WAY FORWARD!</h3>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12 md-space">
<h3 class="term-title">WELCOME TO AKA GYPSY VANNER WORLDWIDE.COM EXPLORE AND ENJOY! </h3>
<p><b>About Transport</b></p>
<p class="about-trext">Once you are registered on the website the price you will be quoted for each horse is unique to you. It represents the estimated total cost of that horse delivered to your location. All transport is carried out to the highest standards, by licensed and approved equine transport companies with an established reputation for excellence. You will be able to track your horse throughout the delivery process. While the horse is being constantly monitored to insure it reaches you in top physical condition.</p>

<p><b>Ethical Breeding and Sales Policy</b></p>
<p class="about-trext">AKA Gypsy Vanner Worldwide, will strive to promote ethical and best practice breeding as a minimum requirement in both its operating model and it efforts to inform its customer base.</p>
<p class="about-trext">Any horse appearing on the site will be required to be micro chipped. As well as being DNA verified and registered.</p>
<p class="about-trext">Where a Dam and a Sire have been selected for a coupling, DNA analysis will be carried out prior to the horses coming together to ensure their bloodlines are free of any crossing, ensuring that the foal produced represents a clean new bloodline. With the potential to go on to be quality breeding stock.</p>
<p class="about-trext">All brood mares will be colour tested prior to appearing on the site. All breeding horses will be DNA checked as individually appropriate.  </p>
<p class="about-trext">AKA Gypsy Vanner Worldwide, will from day one, compile its own stud book as well as keeping a meticulous record of every horse that passes through the site, regardless of whether or not it achieved a sale.</p>
<p class="about-trext">Every effort will be made to ensure that any horse sold through the website, is going to a knowledgeable home, and has a distinct and ethical career path planned for it.</p>
<p class="about-trext">AKA Gypsy/Vanner worldwide will endeavour to ensure that no horse is sold into the hands of quick turnover agents in any country. All horses sold through the site are intended for a long term, loving home. Or they will not be sold!</p>
<p class="about-trext">AKA Gypsy/Vanner will guarantee that they will audit all documentation to ensure that any horse sold through the website, is free of disease, up to date with vaccinations, and in top physical condition prior to export</p>
<p class="about-trext">All horses sold through the website will be inspected and their condition recorded by an independent licensed vet, immediately prior to embarkation of the export process. </p>
